Class Bibliographic

java.lang.Object
model.Bibliographic
All Implemented Interfaces:

Direct Known Subclasses:

public abstract class Bibliographic extends Object implements Comparable<Bibliographic>
The Bibliographic class is an abstract class that contains attributes and methods related to bibliographic products.
